## Performance Metrics

### Protocol KPIs

```solidity
struct ProtocolMetrics {
    uint256 totalUsers;              // Cumulative registered users
    uint256 activeUsers30d;          // Monthly active participants
    uint256 totalAchievements;       // Achievements minted
    uint256 dAppIntegrations;        // Integrated applications
    uint256 totalValueDistributed;   // Economic activity volume
    uint256 governanceProposals;     // Community proposals created
}
```

### Success Indicators

- **User Engagement**: Daily active addresses and interaction frequency
- **Reputation Distribution**: Score distribution and Gini coefficient
- **Cross-Application Usage**: User activity across multiple integrated dApps
- **Economic Velocity**: Transaction volume and value flows
- **Governance Participation**: Voting rates and proposal engagement

